image_analysis.description: This is a single page from a financial disclosure form, specifically OGE Form 278e, for Donald J. Trump. The page, numbered 6 of 51, lists positions he held in various organizations outside the United States Government. The information is presented in a table format.
image_analysis.layout: The document has a header containing the form number, instructions, filer's name, and the part title. The main body consists of a table with seven columns: '#', 'Organization Name', 'City/State', 'Organization Type', 'Position Held', 'From', and 'To'. Below the table, there is a note explaining gaps in the numerical sequence. A document identifier is located in the bottom right corner.
